0&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Popular.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Popular.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 247px) 100vw, 247px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><img data-attachment-id=\"1001\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/11\/balance-changes-and-clarifications\/popular-4\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Popular-1.png?fit=1010%2C1403&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1010,1403\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Popular\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Popular-1.png?fit=216%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Popular-1.png?fit=737%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-1001\" src=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Popular-1.png?resize=252%2C350&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"252\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Popular-1.png?w=1010&amp;ssl=1 1010w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Popular-1.png?resize=216%2C300&amp;ssl=1 216w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Popular-1.png?resize=768%2C1067&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Popular-1.png?resize=737%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 737w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 252px) 100vw, 252px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Popular gets a much needed buff here, going from a continuous effect to something more similar to Summer Programs. In the past, players rarely grabbed Popular, and even if they did it rarely was a good investment. It also was never a good choice to pick up Junior year, and overall was a terrible card. I think the real issue is that friends now are significantly better than friends later because of the engine building aspect of club cards. Hopefully, this change makes Popular more competitive.<\/p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"778\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/08\/sophomore-deck-changes\/hide-homework-2\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Hide-Homework.png?fit=240%2C336&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"240,336\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Hide Homework\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Hide-Homework.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Hide-Homework.png?fit=240%2C336&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-778\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Hide-Homework.png?resize=280%2C392&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"280\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Hide-Homework.png?w=240&amp;ssl=1 240w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Hide-Homework.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 280px) 100vw, 280px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><img data-attachment-id=\"981\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/11\/balance-changes-and-clarifications\/hide-homework-3\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Hide-Homework.png?fit=1000%2C1400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1000,1400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Hide Homework\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Hide-Homework.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Hide-Homework.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-981\" src=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Hide-Homework.png?resize=280%2C392&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"280\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Hide-Homework.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Hide-Homework.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Hide-Homework.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Hide-Homework.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 280px) 100vw, 280px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Hide Homework is one of those cards that got an inadvertent buff from perfect grade bonuses. Due to perfect grade bonuses, this card allowed a player to completely ruin another player&#8217;s investment into their classes. This change is very small, but it now allows players to get an A in a class through other methods, such as cheating. This way, it isn&#8217;t as oppressive as it used to be.<\/p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"600\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/07\/adjusting-cards-part-two\/shadow-students-2\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Shadow-Students-1.png?fit=1000%2C1400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1000,1400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Shadow Students\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Shadow-Students-1.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Shadow-Students-1.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-600\" src=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Shadow-Students-1.png?resize=278%2C389&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"278\" height=\"389\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Shadow-Students-1.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Shadow-Students-1.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Shadow-Students-1.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Shadow-Students-1.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 278px) 100vw, 278px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><img data-attachment-id=\"982\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/11\/balance-changes-and-clarifications\/shadow-students-3\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Shadow-Students.png?fit=1000%2C1400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1000,1400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Shadow Students\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Shadow-Students.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Shadow-Students.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-982\" src=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Shadow-Students.png?resize=279%2C390&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"279\" height=\"390\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Shadow-Students.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Shadow-Students.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Shadow-Students.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Shadow-Students.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 279px) 100vw, 279px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The effect of Shadow Students has never been successfully pulled off before. Let that sink in. It&#8217;s an enticing card, but it is just too unrealistic to have straight A&#8217;s in 3 rounds. I&#8217;m sure that it is theoretically possible, but the conditions were definitely too strict. My hope is that this card will now be a more interesting decision as it will be a lot easier to get 3 A&#8217;s than 4 A&#8217;s.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"402\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/07\/event-cards-next-steps\/talent-show\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Talent-Show.png?fit=240%2C336&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"240,336\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Talent Show\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Talent-Show.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Talent-Show.png?fit=240%2C336&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-402\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Talent-Show.png?resize=271%2C379&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"271\" height=\"379\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Talent-Show.png?w=240&amp;ssl=1 240w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Talent-Show.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 271px) 100vw, 271px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><img data-attachment-id=\"1003\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/11\/balance-changes-and-clarifications\/talent-show-3\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Talent-Show-1.png?fit=1000%2C1400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1000,1400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Talent Show\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Talent-Show-1.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Talent-Show-1.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone  wp-image-1003\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Talent-Show-1.png?resize=269%2C376&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"269\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Talent-Show-1.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Talent-Show-1.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Talent-Show-1.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Talent-Show-1.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 269px) 100vw, 269px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/p>\n<p>I&#8217;m trying to remove all of the cards that use the word &#8220;give&#8221;, as it just becomes really confusing and is kind of unnecessary. In a lot of playtests, players have been giving eachother their cubes and were unsure on whether they should still get friends even if another player had no friends. Thus, this change.<\/p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"616\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/07\/adjusting-cards-part-four\/steal-textbooks-2\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Steal-Textbooks-1.png?fit=1000%2C1400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1000,1400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Steal Textbooks\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Steal-Textbooks-1.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Steal-Textbooks-1.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-616\" src=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Steal-Textbooks-1.png?resize=266%2C372&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"266\" height=\"372\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Steal-Textbooks-1.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Steal-Textbooks-1.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Steal-Textbooks-1.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\