ngth&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Monopolize Lunch Table\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Monopolize-Lunch-Table-1.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Monopolize-Lunch-Table-1.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-987\" src=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Monopolize-Lunch-Table-1.png?resize=319%2C446&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"319\" height=\"446\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Monopolize-Lunch-Table-1.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Monopolize-Lunch-Table-1.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Monopolize-Lunch-Table-1.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Monopolize-Lunch-Table-1.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 319px) 100vw, 319px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Similar to Talent Show, Monopolize Lunch Table&#8217;s &#8220;Take&#8221; was unclear. I also like this effect more as it somewhat shifts the dynamic of Freshman year from avoiding stocking up friends to stocking up some- for Stud Gov Pres and now this card as well.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Let me know what you think of these changes! Thanks for reading, and make sure to subscribe if you enjoy this content.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Hey everybody! I have some new balance changes and text clarifications for you. Let&#8217;s dive right in! Popular gets a much needed buff here, going from a continuous effect to something more similar to Summer Programs. In the past, players rarely grabbed Popular, and even if they did it rarely was a good investment. It &#8230; <a title=\"Balance Changes and Clarifications\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/11\/balance-changes-and-clarifications\/\" aria-label=\"More on Balance Changes and Clarifications\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":1001,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"spay_email":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/11\/Popular-1.png?fit=1010%2C1403&ssl=1","jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":868,"url":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/09\/more-influence-card-changes\/","url_meta":{"origin":979,"position":0},"title":"More Influence Card Changes","date":"September 6, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Hey everyone! I'm in the final phases of tweaking in terms of the influence cards. They have overall been pretty balanced, and people have enjoyed them a lot. However, there were a couple of cards that were consistently passed over, indicating that they were not very desirable, or too confusing.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Daggers High&quot;","img":{"alt_text":"","src":"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/All-Nighter.png?fit=857%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200","width":350,"height":200},"classes":[]},{"id":895,"url":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/09\/play-testing\/","url_meta":{"origin":979,"position":1},"title":"Mega Post! Photos, Balance Changes, and New Rulebook","date":"September 14, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Hey everyone! I've missed a few posts so I wanted to make it up with a mega-post. I've been doing a bunch of play tests recently, and here are a couple photos: The game is in a good place, and I think that it is pretty balanced. With that in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Daggers High&quot;","img":{"alt_text":"","src":"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/IMG_20180908_173329.jpg?fit=1200%2C900&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200","width":350,"height":200},"classes":[]},{"id":1031,"url":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/12\/massive-update\/","url_meta":{"origin":979,"position":2},"title":"Massive update","date":"December 6, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Hey everyone! Lot's of stuff has been happening recently, and so I thought I'd fill everyone in on what's going on! Firstly some playtest photos: \u00a0 Yep, that's right- a new teacher board! In addition, the card art is now 100% complete, colored, upscaled, and at acceptable resolution. One of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Daggers High&quot;","img":{"alt_text":"","src":"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/2p-December-Couch-Potato-Vs-Teachers-Pet.jpg?fit=1200%2C900&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200","width":350,"height":200},"classes":[]},{"id":693,"url":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/08\/influence-cards-pt-2\/","url_meta":{"origin":979,"position":3},"title":"Influence Cards (Pt. 2)","date":"August 11, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Today we will be looking at the Red Bullying Influence Cards! These cards cost Friends to purchase, and tend to hurt other players. \u00a0 This card and Nasty Rumors have gone under a significant change, which is that they now are not immediate effects. This card used to remove 4\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Daggers High&quot;","img":{"alt_text":"","src":"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Nasty-Rumors.png?fit=857%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200","width":350,"height":200},"classes":[]},{"id":880,"url":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/09\/minor-essay-changes\/","url_meta":{"origin":979,"position":4},"title":"Minor Essay Changes","date":"September 7, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Hey everyone! Just wanted to talk about a couple of Essays that were changed today to be more in line with \"Magnum Opus\". Magnum Opus gives 1 RP for every 2 Happiness, rounded down. These two clubs do similar things depending on the number of Stress or Clubs you had.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Daggers High&quot;","img":{"alt_text":"","src":"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Leadership.png?fit=857%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200","width":350,"height":200},"classes":[]},{"id":801,"url":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/08\/straight-a-bonuses\/","url_meta":{"origin":979,"position":5},"title":"Straight A Bonuses","date":"August 23, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Hey everyone! After the changes to Integrity and a couple of the classes, a new player board was in order. English II and PreCalculus now give +5 Teacher Influence instead of +4. The Integrity Track now does not have any RP symbols on it. TOP Physics and TOP Biology swapped\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Daggers High&quot;","img":{"alt_text":"","src":"https:\/\/i2.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Stan-Dard-trying.png?fit=1200%2C956&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200","width":350,"height":200},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/979"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=979"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/979\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1004,"href":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/979\/revisions\/1004"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1001"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=979"}],"w